<chapter id="buttons">
    <title>Wrapper Project Buttons</title> 
    <section>
        <title>Show Off Your Use of the Wrapper</title>
        <para>
            Now you can proudly show off your use of the Java Service Wrapper by
            displaying one of the following buttons on your site.  In addition to
            looking great, they will help your users gain confidence in your
            application, knowing that it is running under the watchful eyes of the
            Java Service Wrapper.
        </para>
        <para>
            All that needs to be done is to choose a button and copy the associated
            HTML into the source of your application's home page.
        </para>
